Name: wmo_wis2_gw_published_total
Description: Number of messages published; grouped by GTS CCCC code

Name: wmo_wis2_gw_gts_received_total
Description: Number of messages received from GTS; grouped by GTS CCCC code (variance with wmo_wis2_gw_published_total indicates processing failure)

Name: wmo_wis2_gw_published_errors_total
Description: Number of errors occurring while processing messages received from GTS; grouped by GTS CCCC code

Name: wmo_wis2_gw_gts_last_received_timestamp_seconds
Description: Timestamp of most recent message received from GTS; grouped by GTS CCCC code
